   EXCLUSIVE-CHINA-TECHNOLOGY (Undated) _ The scientist at the
center of an investigation of whether two U.S. companies improperly
helped China improve its rockets told the Chinese in 1996 that he
would do everything he could to make their rockets the most
reliable in the industry. By Elaine Sciolino and Jeff Gerth.
</P>
<P>
   KOSOVO-RECRUITS (Fierze, Albania) _ Kosovo rebels are having
their ranks bolstered by ethnic Albanians from Germany and
Switzerland. By Chris Hedges. (With graphic.)
