   ISLAM-BOMB-REVIEW _ There is, today at least, no special reason
to believe that Pakistan's newly declared ability to build a
nuclear arsenal will provide a nuclear umbrella for other Islamic
societies, or that those other countries will find it easier to go
nuclear themselves. By Elaine Sciolino. &QL;
</P>
<P>
   ABORTION-REVIEW _ A statistical look around the world on
abortion shows a complex picture. Assuming that cultural
sensitivities are reflected in laws about abortion, there is a
remarkable divide between richer countries and poorer ones where
abortion and its effects are concerned. By Barbara Crosette. &QL;
</P>
<P>
