down on 12,000 Americans _ mostly children, but also 7 postal
employees daily on average _ for a total of more than 4 million dog
bites annually. The cost? Ouch: hundreds of millions of dollars
annually in medical bills and liability claims. A look at some
recent research and literature on the topic.
</P>
