<DATE_TIME> 1998-06-06 15:39 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7435 &Cx1f; taf-z
u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-POLITICAL-BRIEFS-NYT &LR;      06-06 1200
