</P>
<P>
   Coach: Henri Michel, 50. &QL;
</P>
<P>
   Projected finish: First round. &QL;
</P>
<P>
   Comment: A disappointing African Nation's Cup didn't help
Michel's popularity. Failing to reach the second round won't help
his job security.
