</P>
<P>
   ``There is an easy contrast here, with the cover jacket, but it
misreads both the book and Newt's political needs,'' Blankley said.
</P>
<P>
   In the wake of last year's reprimand by the House for violating
ethics rules and a failed effort to depose him as speaker, Gingrich
