land dominated by the passion of the ball. In the game space,
Brazilian football is capable of forgetting even the objective of
scoring, certain that virtue without joy is a contradiction.
Winning the World Cup or not, we are the champions of the passion
aroused by the ball!'' These people are as serious about their
sport as Kentucky fans are about basketball.
