   &UR;  &LR; CUP RECORD: 42-15-16, in 13 appearances. &QL; 
 &UR;  &LR; BEST RESULT: West Germany won in 1954, 1974 and 1990. &QL; 
 &UR;  &LR; PLAYERS YOU MIGHT KNOW: Striker Jurgen Klinsmann, who is expected
to start in his third World Cup, and sweeper Lothar Matthaeus, who
is not expected to start in his record fifth. &QL; 
 &UR;  &LR; PLAYERS YOU SHOULD KNOW: Fullback Jurgen Kohler, midfielders
Christian Ziege, Andreas Moller, Thomas Hassler and Dietmar Hamann
and striker Oliver Bierhoff. &QL; 
